OL,3,CCleverly vows to hold perpetrators to
OL,4,Caccount by updating law on spiking
OL,6,F"We've had something in the region of
OL,7,F560 reported incidents per month. But
OL,8,Fas I said, we know that is
OL,9,Funderreporting.
OL,11,F"We know that we have to protect women
OL,12,Fand girls who are predominantly the
OL,13,Fvictims of this crime type, which is
OL,14,Fwhy we're taking this so seriously."
OL,16,FMr Cleverly accompanied Sussex Police
OL,17,Fofficers on Crawley High Street on
OL,18,FThursday to see the work being done by
OL,19,Fforces to tackle the crime.
