OL,3,CCleverly vows to hold perpetrators to
OL,4,Caccount by updating law on spiking
OL,6,FThe visit comes as the Home Office
OL,7,Fannounced a number of measures in
OL,8,FDecember to tackle spiking, including
OL,9,Ftraining door staff in the night-time
OL,10,Feconomy to spot perpetrators and
OL,11,Finvesting in research into fast
OL,12,Fspiking test kits to help quick
OL,13,Fdetection of spiking by police.
OL,15,FThe cabinet minister added: "We know
OL,16,Fthat with the drugs that are prevalent
OL,17,Fin spiking, that speed is of the
OL,18,Fessence.
