OL,6,FIn December, the Home Secretary was
OL,7,Fforced to apologised for reportedly
OL,8,Fmaking an "ironic joke" about spiking
OL,9,Fhis wife's drink with a date rape drug.
OL,11,FSpeaking to female guests at a Downing
OL,12,FStreet reception, Mr Cleverly said "a
OL,13,Flittle bit of Rohypnol in her drink
OL,14,Fevery night" was "not really illegal
OL,15,Fif it's only a little bit", the Sunday
OL,16,FMirror reported at the time.
